00:00:10.912 --> 00:00:13.748 position:19% line:83% align:start
[RUDOLF] Aileen, due to
the nullification of your

00:00:13.882 --> 00:00:17.351 position:7% line:83% align:start
engagement; your pharmaceutical
and agricultural businesses

00:00:17.484 --> 00:00:20.087 position:24% line:83% align:start
will be taken over
by Prince CÃ©dric.

00:00:20.220 --> 00:00:23.190 position:7% line:83% align:start
First he dishonored me and now
he's stealing my life's work?

00:00:23.323 --> 00:00:25.192 position:16% line:83% align:start
This is your comeuppance
for the contracts

00:00:25.325 --> 00:00:26.628 position:19% line:89% align:start
you carelessly created.

00:00:26.761 --> 00:00:30.297 position:16% line:83% align:start
Unfortunately, this will
cost our family much.

00:00:30.430 --> 00:00:33.400 position:24% line:83% align:start
I-- I'm incredibly
sorry, Father.

00:00:33.535 --> 00:00:35.703 position:5% line:83% align:start
[RUDOLF] I'm willing to dismiss
the issue under the circumstance

00:00:35.837 --> 00:00:38.272 position:30% line:83% align:start
you recoup the
losses before the ball.

00:00:38.405 --> 00:00:40.407 position:24% line:83% align:start
But... that's only
two months from now!

00:00:40.542 --> 00:00:42.109 position:21% line:83% align:start
I raised my daughter
to be a fighter,

00:00:42.242 --> 00:00:44.646 position:27% line:83% align:start
not some sap who
wallows in her worries.

00:00:44.779 --> 00:00:46.346 position:16% line:89% align:start
Now hammer away, darling.

00:00:47.649 --> 00:00:49.784 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
I can tell Father is serious.

00:00:49.918 --> 00:00:52.185 position:21% line:83% align:start
If things progress at
this rate, I'll be ousted

00:00:52.319 --> 00:00:53.721 position:27% line:89% align:start
from the family.

00:02:26.179 --> 00:02:28.950 position:13% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] Step one: make up
the boatloads of money

00:02:29.083 --> 00:02:32.720 position:10% line:83% align:start
that thief of a prince stole
from me and my family.

00:02:33.888 --> 00:02:35.823 position:30% line:89% align:start
Hey! Long time!

00:02:35.957 --> 00:02:38.258 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Jasper! A good day to you, sir.

00:02:38.392 --> 00:02:39.794 position:10% line:89% align:start
You're surprisingly cheerful.

00:02:39.927 --> 00:02:42.329 position:13% line:83% align:start
Is it true that engagement
of yours fell through?

00:02:42.462 --> 00:02:43.665 position:21% line:89% align:start
The rumors are true.

00:02:43.798 --> 00:02:45.499 position:30% line:83% align:start
I decline to be
interviewed any further.

00:02:45.633 --> 00:02:47.200 position:13% line:89% align:start
Can't a guy just say hello?

00:02:47.334 --> 00:02:49.269 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm not interested
in an interview.

00:02:49.403 --> 00:02:51.338 position:19% line:83% align:start
And if I was, know that
my paper always stands

00:02:51.471 --> 00:02:52.940 position:19% line:89% align:start
on the side of justice.

00:02:53.074 --> 00:02:55.442 position:19% line:83% align:start
As your friend, I can't
believe how this panned out.

00:02:55.576 --> 00:02:57.111 position:19% line:83% align:start
You were so devoted to
him and he tossed you

00:02:57.244 --> 00:02:58.813 position:21% line:89% align:start
straight to the curb.

00:03:01.214 --> 00:03:04.018 position:19% line:83% align:start
Moving along, I have a
favor I'd like to ask of you!

00:03:04.152 --> 00:03:05.352 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah?

00:03:07.021 --> 00:03:09.123 position:10% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] And with that, I say
we buckle down and repair

00:03:09.256 --> 00:03:10.591 position:33% line:89% align:start
this castle!

00:03:10.725 --> 00:03:13.094 position:19% line:83% align:start
The funding shall come
from my very own pockets!

00:03:13.226 --> 00:03:15.462 position:19% line:89% align:start
Uh, that's interesting.

00:03:15.596 --> 00:03:17.364 position:19% line:83% align:start
Do you mean to suggest
that we allow humans

00:03:17.497 --> 00:03:18.465 position:30% line:89% align:start
in the castle?

00:03:18.599 --> 00:03:20.535 position:5% line:89% align:start
That's just downright blasphemy!

00:03:20.668 --> 00:03:22.937 position:13% line:83% align:start
I find it more blasphemous
to deprive your lord

00:03:23.071 --> 00:03:24.471 position:13% line:89% align:start
of the castle he deserves.

00:03:24.605 --> 00:03:27.340 position:16% line:83% align:start
Are you too blind to see
the glory of this place?

00:03:27.474 --> 00:03:29.010 position:7% line:89% align:start
And this is why I hate humans!

00:03:29.143 --> 00:03:31.946 position:13% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] Jeez, delusions of
grandeur, don't you think?

00:03:32.080 --> 00:03:33.514 position:19% line:89% align:start
There's a second angle.

00:03:33.648 --> 00:03:35.449 position:13% line:83% align:start
You could also look at this
as a great opportunity

00:03:35.583 --> 00:03:36.851 position:30% line:89% align:start
to help others.

00:03:36.984 --> 00:03:40.054 position:16% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE] "Help others?"
And how would I do that?

00:03:40.188 --> 00:03:41.823 position:21% line:89% align:start
So here's the truth.

00:03:41.956 --> 00:03:45.193 position:5% line:83% align:start
Prince CÃ©dric let several of the
finest workers in the land go.

00:03:45.325 --> 00:03:47.628 position:27% line:83% align:start
I propose we hire
them to fix the castle.

00:03:47.762 --> 00:03:49.831 position:24% line:83% align:start
And why would you,
the daughter of a duke,

00:03:49.964 --> 00:03:52.066 position:19% line:83% align:start
go to such lengths for
those beneath you?

00:03:52.200 --> 00:03:54.502 position:38% line:83% align:start
To help.
These gentlemen need it.

00:03:57.471 --> 00:03:59.107 position:19% line:83% align:start
I assumed you would be
quick to meet my offer

00:03:59.239 --> 00:04:00.541 position:21% line:89% align:start
with refusal. But I--

00:04:00.675 --> 00:04:02.342 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
Do as you wish.

00:04:03.276 --> 00:04:04.679 position:5% line:89% align:start
That went better than expected.

00:04:04.812 --> 00:04:06.748 position:24% line:83% align:start
Keith, in addition
to my subsidy,

00:04:06.881 --> 00:04:09.117 position:16% line:83% align:start
we haven't received your
salary in some time now.

00:04:09.249 --> 00:04:12.120 position:10% line:83% align:start
My lord, it's always been my
suspicion that some noble

00:04:12.252 --> 00:04:13.788 position:16% line:89% align:start
is embezzling our funds.

00:04:13.921 --> 00:04:17.491 position:5% line:83% align:start
Please, look into the issue, and
recover whatever we're owed.

00:04:17.625 --> 00:04:20.061 position:24% line:83% align:start
I will use that sum
to repair the castle.

00:04:20.194 --> 00:04:21.095 position:21% line:89% align:start
Just leave it to me.

00:04:21.229 --> 00:04:22.597 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
You should know.

00:04:22.730 --> 00:04:24.632 position:19% line:83% align:start
It so happens that I've
already tasked Jasper,

00:04:24.766 --> 00:04:26.634 position:16% line:83% align:start
an excellent reporter and
acquaintance of mine,

00:04:26.768 --> 00:04:28.468 position:24% line:83% align:start
with investigating
the missing funds.

00:04:28.603 --> 00:04:31.105 position:13% line:83% align:start
Quite bold to take matters
into your own hands.

00:04:31.239 --> 00:04:32.774 position:5% line:89% align:start
Apologies for any encroachment.

00:04:32.907 --> 00:04:36.144 position:10% line:83% align:start
I merely deemed it the best
course of action for us all.

00:04:36.276 --> 00:04:38.212 position:19% line:83% align:start
Your distaste for being
in the debt of another

00:04:38.345 --> 00:04:39.847 position:13% line:89% align:start
grows increasingly evident.

00:04:39.981 --> 00:04:41.983 position:21% line:83% align:start
Let us turn the lens
of judgment on you.

00:04:42.116 --> 00:04:44.919 position:7% line:83% align:start
Why did you take my suggestion
with such aggressive haste?

00:04:45.052 --> 00:04:47.522 position:21% line:83% align:start
Do you enjoy teasing
undeserving ladies?

00:04:47.655 --> 00:04:49.657 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
Perhaps. Who can say?

00:04:49.791 --> 00:04:52.260 position:16% line:83% align:start
While you're in this mood
of hearing me out,

00:04:52.392 --> 00:04:55.495 position:7% line:83% align:start
I would like to borrow a small
plot of land in your forest.

00:04:55.630 --> 00:04:58.298 position:16% line:83% align:start
There, I would construct
a humble croft.

00:04:58.431 --> 00:04:59.432 position:30% line:89% align:start
Would you now?

00:04:59.567 --> 00:05:01.068 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's fine.

00:05:01.202 --> 00:05:03.971 position:16% line:83% align:start
Anything more will depend
on how sincerely you ask.

00:05:07.875 --> 00:05:10.545 position:19% line:83% align:start
Well, there's no point
in dawdling around!

00:05:10.678 --> 00:05:13.480 position:30% line:83% align:start
Sir Belzebuth,
I require the grand tour.

00:05:13.614 --> 00:05:14.916 position:35% line:89% align:start
One moment.

00:05:15.049 --> 00:05:16.349 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Yes?

00:05:24.424 --> 00:05:26.060 position:24% line:83% align:start
--[RIBBON] Yoo-hoo!
--[AILEEN yelps]

00:05:26.194 --> 00:05:28.930 position:10% line:89% align:start
Uh, hello. We've met before!

00:05:29.063 --> 00:05:30.264 position:16% line:89% align:start
There, that should do it.

00:05:30.397 --> 00:05:32.365 position:24% line:83% align:start
I made your shadow
a demonic gateway.

00:05:32.499 --> 00:05:34.401 position:16% line:83% align:start
Demons can travel through
it as they please.

00:05:34.535 --> 00:05:36.369 position:24% line:83% align:start
What compelled you
to do such a thing?

00:05:36.504 --> 00:05:37.972 position:19% line:83% align:start
With this, you will be
universally accepted

00:05:38.105 --> 00:05:41.341 position:16% line:83% align:start
by all demons, no matter
where your travels take you.

00:05:41.474 --> 00:05:43.644 position:41% line:89% align:start
[barks]

00:05:47.215 --> 00:05:49.884 position:21% line:83% align:start
Seems someone's taken
a fancy to my ribbon.

00:05:50.017 --> 00:05:53.087 position:19% line:83% align:start
Does Ribbon sound like
a suitable name for you?

00:05:53.221 --> 00:05:54.222 position:30% line:89% align:start
[RIBBON barks]

00:05:55.455 --> 00:05:57.525 position:13% line:83% align:start
[JASPER] I've always known
that you existed in a league

00:05:57.658 --> 00:05:59.660 position:33% line:89% align:start
all your own.

00:05:59.794 --> 00:06:01.996 position:24% line:83% align:start
But still, Aileen,
bringing humans

00:06:02.129 --> 00:06:05.233 position:13% line:83% align:start
to the demon lord's castle
to do repair work is a lot,

00:06:05.365 --> 00:06:06.801 position:33% line:89% align:start
even for you.

00:06:06.934 --> 00:06:08.536 position:13% line:83% align:start
Don't you fret, it's within
the realm of the law.

00:06:08.669 --> 00:06:11.873 position:19% line:83% align:start
I stayed up the entire
night making sure of that.

00:06:12.006 --> 00:06:14.242 position:19% line:83% align:start
Prince CÃ©dric's a fool
for letting you go.

00:06:14.374 --> 00:06:16.978 position:21% line:83% align:start
A woman as passionate
as you is hard to come by.

00:06:17.111 --> 00:06:20.014 position:19% line:83% align:start
Flattery? That's rather
out of character.

00:06:22.750 --> 00:06:23.718 position:35% line:83% align:start
[BELZEBUTH]
Woman!

00:06:23.851 --> 00:06:25.353 position:10% line:89% align:start
That's infraction number one!

00:06:25.485 --> 00:06:26.854 position:30% line:89% align:start
Whoa, who's he?

00:06:26.988 --> 00:06:28.189 position:30% line:89% align:start
Sir Belzebuth!

00:06:28.322 --> 00:06:30.725 position:16% line:89% align:start
Hey! Listen close, human!

00:06:30.858 --> 00:06:31.993 position:38% line:89% align:start
Uh, yes?

00:06:32.126 --> 00:06:34.328 position:16% line:83% align:start
If you continue to offend
our lord in his home,

00:06:34.461 --> 00:06:38.266 position:13% line:83% align:start
his winds will blow you out
and into the next kingdom!

00:06:38.398 --> 00:06:41.468 position:13% line:83% align:start
Jasper, when did you manage
to disgruntle Lord Claude?

00:06:41.602 --> 00:06:43.470 position:38% line:83% align:start
Beats me!
I've yet to meet the guy!

00:06:43.604 --> 00:06:47.875 position:10% line:83% align:start
Then what in the world could
that spectacle have been about?

00:06:48.009 --> 00:06:50.978 position:10% line:83% align:start
This bluster certainly isn't
convenient for our work.

00:06:51.112 --> 00:06:53.247 position:5% line:83% align:start
If it turns out all those rumors
that the demon lord's

00:06:53.381 --> 00:06:57.985 position:7% line:83% align:start
emotions affect the weather are
true, then that would mean--

00:06:59.320 --> 00:07:00.588 position:21% line:89% align:start
That would mean what?

00:07:00.721 --> 00:07:01.956 position:38% line:83% align:start
[JASPER]
Nothing yet.

00:07:02.089 --> 00:07:04.125 position:24% line:83% align:start
Leaking unverified
information goes against

00:07:04.258 --> 00:07:06.193 position:13% line:89% align:start
my journalistic integrity.

00:07:08.229 --> 00:07:09.697 position:33% line:89% align:start
They're here.

00:07:09.830 --> 00:07:11.732 position:7% line:83% align:start
You may have a lot of enemies,
but there's something

00:07:11.866 --> 00:07:14.101 position:27% line:83% align:start
to be said about
your choice of ally.

00:07:14.235 --> 00:07:16.938 position:16% line:83% align:start
You should choose quality
over quantity, right?

00:07:18.239 --> 00:07:20.942 position:16% line:89% align:start
Hello Denis! Luc! Quartz!

00:07:21.075 --> 00:07:23.711 position:21% line:83% align:start
Even Isaac is willing
to lend a hand!

00:07:23.844 --> 00:07:25.513 position:21% line:83% align:start
There isn't one of us
here who hasn't worried

00:07:25.646 --> 00:07:26.948 position:21% line:89% align:start
over your wellbeing.

00:07:27.081 --> 00:07:28.516 position:21% line:83% align:start
Allow me to nip those
thoughts in the bud

00:07:28.649 --> 00:07:30.384 position:24% line:83% align:start
as there is nothing
to worry about!

00:07:30.518 --> 00:07:34.055 position:27% line:83% align:start
[sighs] Typical.
You're still you.

00:07:35.089 --> 00:07:37.825 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'm ever so grateful you chose
to come, Denis.

00:07:37.959 --> 00:07:40.728 position:10% line:83% align:start
Having a genius architect on
board brings great comfort.

00:07:40.861 --> 00:07:42.997 position:35% line:83% align:start
All right!
What a thrilling chance to play!

00:07:43.130 --> 00:07:45.232 position:27% line:83% align:start
I'm so sorry you
were let go, Luc.

00:07:45.366 --> 00:07:47.268 position:13% line:83% align:start
It pains me so to know how
close you were to seeing

00:07:47.401 --> 00:07:50.404 position:10% line:83% align:start
the results of your medicinal
research come to fruition.

00:07:50.538 --> 00:07:51.939 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's fine!

00:07:52.073 --> 00:07:53.307 position:13% line:83% align:start
The doctor in me is looking
forward to perusing

00:07:53.441 --> 00:07:55.576 position:27% line:83% align:start
the demon lord's
wealth of flora!

00:07:55.710 --> 00:07:58.212 position:19% line:89% align:start
You must be overjoyed!

00:07:58.346 --> 00:07:59.714 position:10% line:89% align:start
He's still a touch depressed.

00:07:59.847 --> 00:08:01.849 position:16% line:83% align:start
Imagine being a botanist
and having all the plants

00:08:01.983 --> 00:08:04.218 position:13% line:83% align:start
you've grown ripped away by
someone who doesn't know

00:08:04.352 --> 00:08:06.020 position:21% line:89% align:start
how to care for them.

00:08:06.153 --> 00:08:09.290 position:7% line:83% align:start
After all that, you're willing
to work for me again?

00:08:09.423 --> 00:08:11.826 position:10% line:83% align:start
If necessary, we can develop
an untraceable poison

00:08:11.959 --> 00:08:13.694 position:7% line:89% align:start
for you to use as you see fit.

00:08:13.828 --> 00:08:15.262 position:24% line:83% align:start
Right? What do you
say, Lord Isaac?

00:08:15.396 --> 00:08:17.565 position:10% line:83% align:start
I want not a thing to do with
your assassination plots

00:08:17.698 --> 00:08:18.532 position:30% line:89% align:start
on the prince!

00:08:18.666 --> 00:08:20.201 position:21% line:89% align:start
You downright quack!

00:08:20.334 --> 00:08:22.937 position:10% line:83% align:start
The demon forest may present
us with the perfect ingredients.

00:08:23.070 --> 00:08:24.305 position:33% line:89% align:start
Pure madness.

00:08:24.438 --> 00:08:26.440 position:13% line:83% align:start
Better yet, I could build a
bridge rigged to collapse

00:08:26.574 --> 00:08:28.676 position:16% line:83% align:start
under a certain princely
amount of weight!

00:08:28.809 --> 00:08:30.344 position:16% line:89% align:start
Build yourself a muzzle!

00:08:30.478 --> 00:08:33.814 position:5% line:83% align:start
Gentlemen! Assassination is fun,
but let's focus on the task

00:08:33.948 --> 00:08:35.082 position:38% line:89% align:start
at hand!

00:08:37.351 --> 00:08:38.753 position:44% line:89% align:start
Wow!

00:08:38.886 --> 00:08:40.454 position:13% line:83% align:start
You've surpassed the bounds
of my imagination!

00:08:40.588 --> 00:08:41.756 position:35% line:89% align:start
Who's that?

00:08:41.889 --> 00:08:43.190 position:24% line:83% align:start
Keith, one of Lord
Claude's aides.

00:08:43.324 --> 00:08:44.558 position:44% line:89% align:start
Who?

00:08:44.692 --> 00:08:46.127 position:24% line:83% align:start
Don't fear, for I'm
an ordinary human.

00:08:46.260 --> 00:08:47.728 position:21% line:89% align:start
Quite unlike you lot.

00:08:47.862 --> 00:08:50.531 position:10% line:83% align:start
You are human, but I wouldn't
describe you as ordinary.

00:08:50.664 --> 00:08:52.166 position:38% line:83% align:start
[JASPER]
So, you've done your research.

00:08:52.299 --> 00:08:55.136 position:13% line:83% align:start
That falls well within the
territory of my occupation here.

00:08:55.269 --> 00:08:58.072 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm frequently gathering
information for my lord.

00:09:00.174 --> 00:09:02.810 position:10% line:83% align:start
We would be wise to a bring
our lollygagging to a close.

00:09:02.943 --> 00:09:05.813 position:19% line:83% align:start
Lord Claude is growing
increasingly upset.

00:09:12.753 --> 00:09:14.722 position:13% line:89% align:start
I bring you... our guests.

00:09:26.033 --> 00:09:29.236 position:19% line:89% align:start
What a cultivated look.

00:09:29.370 --> 00:09:32.740 position:10% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE] I have but one rule
which requires your adherence.

00:09:32.873 --> 00:09:34.742 position:30% line:83% align:start
Do not harm the
demons you'll find here

00:09:34.875 --> 00:09:37.078 position:7% line:89% align:start
or threaten their way of life.

00:09:37.211 --> 00:09:39.947 position:10% line:83% align:start
Keep in mind I know all that
happens within this barrier;

00:09:40.081 --> 00:09:42.216 position:21% line:83% align:start
commit the most minor
infraction, I will see it,

00:09:42.349 --> 00:09:44.318 position:21% line:83% align:start
and you will be dealt
with accordingly.

00:09:44.452 --> 00:09:45.986 position:38% line:89% align:start
Question.

00:09:46.120 --> 00:09:48.789 position:10% line:83% align:start
Precisely what part of this
castle is in need of repair?

00:09:52.493 --> 00:09:53.761 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ALL gasp]

00:09:55.963 --> 00:09:57.665 position:16% line:89% align:start
Where did the ceiling go?

00:09:57.798 --> 00:09:59.667 position:24% line:89% align:start
Huh? What is this?

00:10:04.506 --> 00:10:06.941 position:19% line:83% align:start
As you can see, there's
much work to be done.

00:10:07.074 --> 00:10:09.743 position:21% line:83% align:start
I've been using magic
to hold the place together.

00:10:13.147 --> 00:10:15.216 position:30% line:83% align:start
