comfortable for demons.

00:10:20.354 --> 00:10:22.690 position:16% line:83% align:start
[DENIS] Then could I talk
to the demons directly?

00:10:22.823 --> 00:10:24.792 position:24% line:83% align:start
Belzebuth, please
interpret for him.

00:10:24.925 --> 00:10:26.595 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yes, your lordship.

00:10:26.727 --> 00:10:29.598 position:27% line:83% align:start
