a decision is required.

00:10:29.730 --> 00:10:30.965 position:35% line:89% align:start
Dismissed.

00:10:31.098 --> 00:10:32.299 position:35% line:83% align:start
[BELZEBUTH]
Demons are surprisingly...

00:10:32.433 --> 00:10:33.968 position:38% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN]
Lord Claude?

00:10:34.101 --> 00:10:36.804 position:19% line:83% align:start
You seem a smidgen more
on edge than usual.

00:10:38.540 --> 00:10:40.074 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
And?

00:10:40.207 --> 00:10:43.777 position:5% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] I was merely curious if
something was bothering you.

00:10:43.911 --> 00:10:47.715 position:10% line:83% align:start
