simplest of gowns.

00:11:05.567 --> 00:11:07.034 position:24% line:89% align:start
Rather paltry, no?

00:11:07.168 --> 00:11:10.337 position:13% line:89% align:start
Paltry? Spoken like a man.

00:11:10.471 --> 00:11:12.907 position:13% line:83% align:start
Don't you know that dresses
are womankind's battle armor?

00:11:13.040 --> 00:11:14.308 position:21% line:83% align:start
Perhaps someone like
you has the confidence

00:11:14.441 --> 00:11:16.645 position:33% line:83% align:start
