au naturel, but not I!

00:11:16.777 --> 00:11:19.346 position:27% line:83% align:start
No. I'll keep my
clothing on, thanks.

00:11:19.480 --> 00:11:21.516 position:21% line:83% align:start
And! The main reason
I invest in attire

00:11:21.650 --> 00:11:24.018 position:19% line:83% align:start
is so I may confidently
stand by your side!

00:11:24.151 --> 00:11:26.754 position:13% line:83% align:start
No matter the elegance with
which your exterior is draped,

00:11:26.887 --> 00:11:29.256 position:21% line:83% align:start
