burns the same.

00:11:30.724 --> 00:11:33.928 position:5% line:83% align:start
Be that as it may, I understand
the logic behind your reasoning.

00:11:34.061 --> 00:11:35.564 position:16% line:89% align:start
I beg you, wait a moment.

00:11:35.696 --> 00:11:39.133 position:10% line:83% align:start
Tell me, what was instigating
your unhappiness earlier?

00:11:40.968 --> 00:11:42.136 position:35% line:89% align:start
Who knows?

00:11:42.269 --> 00:11:44.371 position:27% line:83% align:start
I can't say with
much certainty myself.

00:11:44.506 --> 00:11:45.773 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:11:47.676 --> 00:11:49.243 position:16% line:89% align:start
Gone without a trace, eh?

00:11:49.376 --> 00:11:50.679 position:38% line:89% align:start
Peculiar.

00:11:50.811 --> 00:11:52.213 position:41% line:83% align:start
[KEITH]
You have nothing to worry about.

00:11:52.346 --> 00:11:54.982 position:21% line:83% align:start
