00:12:08.896 --> 00:12:09.863 position:41% line:89% align:start
Grand!

00:12:09.997 --> 00:12:11.566 position:19% line:89% align:start
This way. Come on, kid.

00:12:11.700 --> 00:12:14.401 position:10% line:83% align:start
