00:12:39.893 --> 00:12:41.395 position:27% line:89% align:start
Don't be foolish.

00:12:41.529 --> 00:12:43.998 position:13% line:83% align:start
Now that Prince CÃ©dric has
ownership over the business,

00:12:44.131 --> 00:12:46.033 position:19% line:83% align:start
he'll no doubt throw a
complete and utter tantrum

00:12:46.166 --> 00:12:48.703 position:7% line:83% align:start
