in the same vein as him.

00:12:48.836 --> 00:12:51.872 position:13% line:83% align:start
What's more, he's connected
enough to shut us down.

00:12:52.006 --> 00:12:53.841 position:19% line:89% align:start
We need something new.

00:12:53.974 --> 00:12:56.143 position:13% line:89% align:start
What we need are cosmetics.

00:12:56.277 --> 00:12:59.246 position:7% line:83% align:start
We ladies are willing to spend
much in the pursuit of beauty.

00:12:59.380 --> 00:13:01.882 position:16% line:83% align:start
We'll use that knowledge
to our favor.

00:13:02.016 --> 00:13:03.652 position:41% line:83% align:start
I see.
That's not a bad idea.

00:13:03.784 --> 00:13:06.688 position:7% line:83% align:start
