my realm of expertise.

00:13:06.820 --> 00:13:09.990 position:10% line:83% align:start
You use salves and scrubs on
chapped and blistered skin, yes?

00:13:10.124 --> 00:13:12.727 position:13% line:83% align:start
Just consider this another
form of dermal healing.

00:13:12.860 --> 00:13:14.529 position:27% line:89% align:start
Interesting spin.

00:13:14.663 --> 00:13:16.163 position:21% line:89% align:start
Let's give it a try.

00:13:16.297 --> 00:13:18.399 position:30% line:83% align:start
I will test our
products personally.

00:13:18.533 --> 00:13:20.901 position:13% line:83% align:start
The sight of me all done up
standing beside Lord Claude

00:13:21.035 --> 00:13:22.369 position:5% line:89% align:start
will make a great advertisement.

00:13:22.504 --> 00:13:26.407 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ISAAC] Indeed, his
beauty is otherworldly.

00:13:26.541 --> 00:13:28.108 position:27% line:83% align:start
I was hoping our
cosmetics could raise me

00:13:28.242 --> 00:13:30.210 position:19% line:83% align:start
to the playing field of
your gentleman crush.

00:13:30.344 --> 00:13:32.146 position:10% line:89% align:start
Now that's a selfish motive!

00:13:32.279 --> 00:13:33.480 position:38% line:89% align:start
So be it!

00:13:33.615 --> 00:13:35.650 position:13% line:83% align:start
I will not lose any beauty
pageants to my escort!

00:13:36.618 --> 00:13:38.687 position:19% line:83% align:start
If this is an accurate
portrayal of  all womenkind,

00:13:38.852 --> 00:13:40.187 position:19% line:89% align:start
we're sure to be rich.

00:13:42.356 --> 00:13:43.957 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CÃDRIC]
What's she doing?

00:13:44.091 --> 00:13:46.393 position:13% line:83% align:start
Can't say, but she gathered
up all the laborers

00:13:46.528 --> 00:13:47.961 position:21% line:83% align:start
you recently released
and brought them

00:13:48.095 --> 00:13:49.597 position:13% line:89% align:start
to the demon lord's castle.

00:13:49.731 --> 00:13:51.932 position:13% line:83% align:start
I fear there's a scheme at
the center of her newfound

00:13:52.066 --> 00:13:54.001 position:16% line:89% align:start
