00:14:09.383 --> 00:14:11.619 position:10% line:89% align:start
Yes! It's the perfect scent!

00:14:11.753 --> 00:14:13.755 position:10% line:83% align:start
[LUC] I couldn't have done it
without the steam distiller

00:14:13.887 --> 00:14:15.657 position:13% line:89% align:start
