00:14:25.999 --> 00:14:27.201 position:41% line:89% align:start
Indeed!

00:14:27.334 --> 00:14:28.570 position:19% line:83% align:start
Using Isaac's documents
for a basis,

00:14:28.703 --> 00:14:30.404 position:24% line:83% align:start
