00:14:57.732 --> 00:14:59.400 position:24% line:83% align:start
Return from whence
you came right now!

00:14:59.534 --> 00:15:03.671 position:24% line:83% align:start
Cookies! Brownies!
Cakes and pies and--

00:15:03.805 --> 00:15:05.239 position:19% line:89% align:start
Don't you chant at me!

00:15:05.372 --> 00:15:08.510 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'll bake you confections
once things calm down!

00:15:08.643 --> 00:15:09.644 position:38% line:83% align:start
[ALMOND]
...tyrant!

00:15:09.778 --> 00:15:11.311 position:38% line:83% align:start
[CLAUDE]
Don't bother her.

00:15:11.445 --> 00:15:13.748 position:13% line:83% align:start
Well! It's assuring to see
they're obedient to someone

00:15:13.882 --> 00:15:15.349 position:24% line:89% align:start
at the very least.

00:15:15.482 --> 00:15:16.950 position:7% line:83% align:start
I'm delighted to report to you
that we got to the bottom

00:15:17.084 --> 00:15:18.452 position:24% line:83% align:start
