00:15:19.821 --> 00:15:21.121 position:38% line:89% align:start
Goodness!

00:15:21.255 --> 00:15:23.290 position:24% line:83% align:start
Your friend Jasper
is incredibly talented!

00:15:23.424 --> 00:15:25.192 position:10% line:83% align:start
That's curious, as I received
word you obtained

00:15:25.325 --> 00:15:27.494 position:21% line:83% align:start
most of the evidence
on your own.

00:15:27.629 --> 00:15:29.329 position:24% line:83% align:start
Once you uncovered
the culprit's identity,

00:15:29.463 --> 00:15:31.833 position:16% line:83% align:start
why didn't you let Jasper
denounce them in the press?

00:15:31.965 --> 00:15:33.133 position:41% line:89% align:start
Simple.

00:15:33.267 --> 00:15:34.636 position:30% line:83% align:start
Some things are
best kept private.

00:15:34.769 --> 00:15:37.304 position:13% line:83% align:start
The public can't know that
the demon lord was poor!

00:15:39.139 --> 00:15:41.408 position:16% line:83% align:start
[DENIS gasps] You've gone
and hurt his feelings!

00:15:41.543 --> 00:15:43.210 position:41% line:83% align:start
[KEITH]
He won't be poor any longer!

00:15:43.343 --> 00:15:44.612 position:19% line:89% align:start
Money's no concern now.

00:15:44.746 --> 00:15:46.881 position:16% line:83% align:start
And preparations for the
ball are going smoothly.

00:15:47.014 --> 00:15:49.784 position:10% line:83% align:start
You're able to avoid falling
from his favor until then.

00:15:49.918 --> 00:15:51.185 position:41% line:89% align:start
Right?

00:15:52.186 --> 00:15:54.354 position:21% line:83% align:start
Right! I'll certainly
give it my all.

00:15:54.488 --> 00:15:57.926 position:7% line:83% align:start
We look forward to the big day,
don't we, Lord Claude?

00:15:58.058 --> 00:15:59.527 position:19% line:89% align:start
Don't we, Lord Claude?

00:16:00.762 --> 00:16:02.296 position:30% line:89% align:start
Not especially.

00:16:03.598 --> 00:16:05.633 position:16% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] Why, because he
doesn't believe my appearance

00:16:05.767 --> 00:16:07.702 position:5% line:89% align:start
