00:16:19.313 --> 00:16:21.516 position:10% line:89% align:start
Work to your highest caliber!

00:16:21.649 --> 00:16:22.750 position:38% line:89% align:start
Poor man.

00:16:22.884 --> 00:16:24.819 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's a shame to be foiled
by your own naivetÃ©.

