00:16:40.200 --> 00:16:43.203 position:13% line:83% align:start
[gasps] You can utilize my
shadow as well?

00:16:43.337 --> 00:16:45.372 position:5% line:89% align:start
That would've been nice to know.

00:16:45.507 --> 00:16:46.240 position:41% line:89% align:start
Human.

00:16:46.373 --> 00:16:47.842 position:13% line:89% align:start
I come here with a request.

00:16:47.976 --> 00:16:50.277 position:19% line:83% align:start
