uninvited at the dead of night

00:16:50.410 --> 00:16:52.547 position:16% line:83% align:start
is a nearly unforgivable
transgression.

00:16:52.680 --> 00:16:54.682 position:30% line:83% align:start
But I'll turn a
blind eye this time.

00:16:54.816 --> 00:16:56.216 position:19% line:89% align:start
What is it you require?

00:16:56.350 --> 00:16:58.820 position:19% line:83% align:start
If our lord is going to
be attending this ball,

00:16:58.953 --> 00:17:00.722 position:7% line:89% align:start
then I wish to attend as well.

00:17:00.855 --> 00:17:02.724 position:10% line:83% align:start
Aides are welcome, but you'll
be asked to stand off

00:17:02.857 --> 00:17:04.291 position:27% line:89% align:start
toward the side.

00:17:04.424 --> 00:17:05.760 position:21% line:89% align:start
That's fine with me.

00:17:05.894 --> 00:17:08.161 position:16% line:83% align:start
I only want to go because
the detestable humans

00:17:08.295 --> 00:17:10.430 position:27% line:83% align:start
