lord will be there.

00:17:10.565 --> 00:17:16.036 position:5% line:83% align:start
Though Lord Claude is strong, he
is not necessarily invulnerable.

00:17:17.805 --> 00:17:19.507 position:19% line:83% align:start
I have heard that if I
don't want to shame him

00:17:19.641 --> 00:17:21.809 position:13% line:83% align:start
