00:17:23.243 --> 00:17:25.880 position:24% line:83% align:start
Think you can help
me achieve this?

00:17:26.014 --> 00:17:27.649 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'd be honored to.

00:17:27.782 --> 00:17:30.785 position:5% line:83% align:start
I'll arm you with all the tricks
and trades of high society!

00:17:30.919 --> 00:17:33.021 position:21% line:89% align:start
Ha! I'm in your debt!

00:17:33.186 --> 00:17:34.789 position:30% line:83% align:start
Lord Claude is
lucky to have you.

00:17:34.923 --> 00:17:37.357 position:24% line:83% align:start
From all I've seen,
he's very well loved.

00:17:37.491 --> 00:17:41.829 position:13% line:83% align:start
I find it peculiar so many
are wary to get close to him.

00:17:41.963 --> 00:17:44.097 position:13% line:89% align:start
Wary to get close to, huh?

00:17:44.231 --> 00:17:46.701 position:16% line:83% align:start
If I remember correctly,
these two don't get along

00:17:46.834 --> 00:17:48.201 position:27% line:89% align:start
