training as soon as I can.

00:17:57.645 --> 00:17:58.312 position:35% line:89% align:start
Of course.

00:17:58.445 --> 00:18:00.080 position:19% line:89% align:start
For your first lesson,

00:18:02.482 --> 00:18:05.252 position:16% line:83% align:start
