keep the workspace tidy, got it?

00:18:13.427 --> 00:18:14.896 position:38% line:83% align:start
[WORKERS]
Got it!

00:18:15.029 --> 00:18:17.164 position:21% line:83% align:start
[AILEEN] Everyone is
working so diligently.

00:18:17.297 --> 00:18:20.068 position:16% line:83% align:start
